{
  "name": "Bestial Fury Kick",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Taijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You perform a devastating round house kick with enough force to even effect creatures 10 feet away from you. Make a melee taijutsu attack targeting a creature in range On a hit, you deal your [Unarmed Damage] + 2d4 and the target must make a Strength saving throw, being pushed back 10 feet on a failed save.</p><p>If this jutsu is used as a Finisher, all creatures in a 15- foot cone directly in front of you must make a Strength saving throw, taking your [Unarmed Damage] + 2d6, being push back 10 feet and falling prone on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful save.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and damage by 1d4 or 1d6.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
